@b-slim before this patch, user can use namespaced lookup by setting `lookup` of `LookupDimensionSpec` as

```
{
  "type":"namespace",
  "namepace":"DB1"
}
```

If this issue is resolved, user can also specify lookup map name within the namespace

```
{
  "type":"namespace",
  "namepace":"DB1",
  "mapName":"CtoD"
}
```
